\"to\": 4511}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unless the climber is competing in a specific discipline like ice climbing or canyoneering, or if they have a specific body type-children typically require a kid's harness, for example-then they can just pick a harness based on comfort.\", \"from\": 4514, \"to\": 4750, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the climber\", \"from\": 4521, \"to\": 4532}, {\"ngram\": \"a specific discipline\", \"from\": 4549, \"to\": 4570}, {\"ngram\": \"ice climbing\", \"from\": 4576, \"to\": 4588}, {\"ngram\": \"canyoneering\", \"from\": 4592, \"to\": 4604}, {\"ngram\": \"a specific body type-children\", \"from\": 4622, \"to\": 4651}, {\"ngram\": \"a kid's harness\", \"from\": 4670, \"to\": 4685}, {\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 4691, \"to\": 4698}, {\"ngram\": \"a harness\", \"from\": 4723, \"to\": 4732}, {\"ngram\": \"comfort\", \"from\": 4742, \"to\": 4749}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I sit in my harness a lot of the day when I am training, so comfort is probably the most important thing I look for in a harness,\\\" Grupper says.\", \"from\": 4751, \"to\": 4896, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my harness\", \"from\": 4761, \"to\": 4771}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 4781, \"to\": 4788}, {\"ngram\": \"comfort\", \"from\": 4812, \"to\": 4819}, {\"ngram\": \"the most important thing\", \"from\": 4832, \"to\": 4856}, {\"ngram\": \"a harness\", \"from\": 4871, \"to\": 4880}, {\"ngram\": \"Grupper\", \"from\": 4883, \"to\": 4890}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He uses the Trango Horizon.\", \"from\": 4897, \"to\": 4924, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Trango Horizon\", \"from\": 4905, \"to\": 4923}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It has extra loops for attaching things to it, it's intuitive to use, and it's a safe brand that I trust.\\\"\", \"from\": 4925, \"to\": 5032, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"extra loops\", \"from\": 4933, \"to\": 4944}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 4959, \"to\": 4965}, {\"ngram\": \"a safe brand\", \"from\": 5005, \"to\": 5017}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Full disclosure: Trango is one of Grupper's sponsors and the representation that arranged this interview.\", \"from\": 5033, \"to\": 5138, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Trango\", \"from\": 5050, \"to\": 5056}, {\"ngram\": \"Grupper's sponsors\", \"from\": 5067, \"to\": 5085}, {\"ngram\": \"the representation\", \"from\": 5090, \"to\": 5108}, {\"ngram\": \"this interview\", \"from\": 5123, \"to\": 5137}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sterling When you are climbing, your rope is your best friend.\", \"from\": 5142, \"to\": 5205, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sterling\", \"from\": 5142, \"to\": 5150}, {\"ngram\": \"your rope\", \"from\": 5174, \"to\": 5183}, {\"ngram\": \"your best friend\", \"from\": 5187, \"to\": 5203}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the item that keeps you from falling and hitting the ground!\", \"from\": 5206, \"to\": 5271, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the item\", \"from\": 5211, \"to\": 5219}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 5260, \"to\": 5270}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are many different kinds of ropes, but for sport climbing, you want a single, dynamic rope that will stretch and give as you fall.\", \"from\": 5272, \"to\": 5408, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many different kinds\", \"from\": 5282, \"to\": 5302}, {\"ngram\": \"ropes\", \"from\": 5306, \"to\": 5311}, {\"ngram\": \"sport climbing\", \"from\": 5321, \"to\": 5335}, {\"ngram\": \"a single, dynamic rope\", \"from\": 5346, \"to\": 5368}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A thicker rope is more durable, but harder to carry and maneuver into the draws.\", \"from\": 5409, \"to\": 5489, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A thicker rope\", \"from\": 5409, \"to\": 5423}, {\"ngram\": \"the draws\", \"from\": 5479, \"to\": 5488}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Also, keep your rope's length in mind-you want the pitch that you are climbing to be half the length of your rope in order to descend safely.\", \"from\": 5490, \"to\": 5631, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your rope's length\", \"from\": 5501, \"to\": 5519}, {\"ngram\": \"mind\", \"from\": 5523, \"to\": 5527}, {\"ngram\": \"the pitch\", \"from\": 5537, \"to\": 5546}, {\"ngram\": \"half the length\", \"from\": 5575, \"to\": 5590}, {\"ngram\": \"your rope\", \"from\": 5594, \"to\": 5603}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 5607, \"to\": 5612}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So if you are climbing a 30-meter route, you need a 60-meter rope.\", \"from\": 5632, \"to\": 5698, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a 30-meter route\", \"from\": 5655, \"to\": 5671}, {\"ngram\": \"a 60-meter rope\", \"from\": 5682, \"to\": 5697}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Grupper likes Sterling's Aero Rope because, with a thickness of 9.2 millimeters, it's extremely thin and light compared to other ropes.\", \"from\": 5700, \"to\": 5835, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5714, \"end\": 5722, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pound_sterling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8283509132933584e-45, \"text\": \"Sterling\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pound_sterling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pound_sterling\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Grupper\", \"from\": 5700, \"to\": 5707}, {\"ngram\": \"a thickness\", \"from\": 5749, \"to\": 5760}, {\"ngram\": \"9.2 millimeters\", \"from\": 5764, \"to\": 5779}, {\"ngram\": \"other ropes\", \"from\": 5823, \"to\": 5834}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The fibers are also treated with what Sterling callsa Xeros processthat keeps it clean and dry and allows it to glide more easily through your rappel or belay device.\", \"from\": 5836, \"to\": 6002, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5874, \"end\": 5882, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pound_sterling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8283509132933584e-45, \"text\": \"Sterling\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pound_sterling\", 