l air conditioners for the warm-up area itself,\\\" which is indoors, while the venue is outside, says Grupper.\", \"from\": 7255, \"to\": 7384, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"personal air conditioners\", \"from\": 7269, \"to\": 7294}, {\"ngram\": \"the warm-up area\", \"from\": 7299, \"to\": 7315}, {\"ngram\": \"indoors\", \"from\": 7334, \"to\": 7341}, {\"ngram\": \"the venue\", \"from\": 7349, \"to\": 7358}, {\"ngram\": \"Grupper\", \"from\": 7376, \"to\": 7383}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do think it's pretty interesting how the sport is evolving to meet the demands of climate change.\\\"\", \"from\": 7385, \"to\": 7486, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 7425, \"to\": 7434}, {\"ngram\": \"the demands\", \"from\": 7455, \"to\": 7466}, {\"ngram\": \"climate change\", \"from\": 7470, \"to\": 7484}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Luckily, most of the teams are providing personal cooling equipment, but Grupper has been practicing while wearing an ice vest, just to see what it feels like.\", \"from\": 7488, \"to\": 7647, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the teams\", \"from\": 7505, \"to\": 7514}, {\"ngram\": \"personal cooling equipment\", \"from\": 7529, \"to\": 7555}, {\"ngram\": \"Grupper\", \"from\": 7561, \"to\": 7568}, {\"ngram\": \"an ice vest\", \"from\": 7603, \"to\": 7614}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nike has made specific ice vests for Team USA for this year's Olympics; this is not one, but it has four refreezable ice packs in pockets that can be easily transported.\", \"from\": 7648, \"to\": 7817, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7648, \"end\": 7652, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"score\": 0.9999997872637549, \"rank\": 2.1273629611324062e-07, \"text\": \"Nike\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\"}, {\"begin\": 7685, \"end\": 7693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resourc